name: Selene, the Sacred Sovereign of Magic
desc:
2+ monsters, including a Spellcaster monster
If this card is Link Summoned: Place Spell Counters on this card equal to the number of Spells on the field and in the GYs. While an "Endymion" card is on the field, your opponent's monsters cannot target this card for attacks. Once per turn, during the Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can remove 3 Spell Counters from your field; Special Summon 1 Spellcaster monster from your hand or GY in Defense Position to your zone this card points to.
